278
00:14:00,339 --> 00:14:02,364
We had perfectly normal
conversations.

279
00:14:02,474 --> 00:14:04,203
And so I just left her upstairs.

280
00:14:04,376 --> 00:14:07,868
And then about 3:00 or 4:00
in the morning,

281
00:14:07,980 --> 00:14:09,880
Macall and her boyfriend
came upstairs

282
00:14:09,982 --> 00:14:12,314
