on the kitchen floor.

283
00:14:12,418 --> 00:14:14,477
You know, then she started
breathing a little funny.

284
00:14:14,587 --> 00:14:16,714
I'm like, "We should
seriously call somebody."

285
00:14:16,822 --> 00:14:18,483
You know, she's unconscious.

286
00:14:18,591 --> 00:14:20,855
We can't even get her
