292
00:14:35,507 --> 00:14:40,638
And Jasen said,
"We ought to call 911."

293
00:14:40,746 --> 00:14:42,805
And Macall said no.

294
00:14:42,915 --> 00:14:44,780
I was scared to death.

295
00:14:44,884 --> 00:14:46,909
Never seen someone like that
