296
00:14:47,019 --> 00:14:49,886
Not knowing what's wrong and not
knowing it's a drug overdose.

297
00:14:49,989 --> 00:14:52,082
You know, not knowing
how to help this person.

298
00:14:52,191 --> 00:14:55,558
Yeah, calling 911,
that was my first thing,

299
00:14:55,661 --> 00:14:56,719
but I was told not to.

300
00:14:56,829 --> 00:14:59,491
And, so, trying to help them
