316
00:16:00,059 --> 00:16:01,048
Buried it.

317
00:16:01,160 --> 00:16:06,427
Tried to cover it with weeds
and twigs and all those things.

318
00:16:07,199 --> 00:16:11,033
And then Tuesday came,
