320
00:16:15,140 --> 00:16:17,472
wanting to talk about
what was going on.

321
00:16:17,576 --> 00:16:18,873
<i>And...</i>

322
00:16:19,945 --> 00:16:24,075
<i>...</i> someone said, "Did you know
