323
00:16:25,117 --> 00:16:29,850
And I just thought,
"Well, that's it, then.

324
00:16:29,955 --> 00:16:36,155
I don't need to talk anymore
on the TV, because that's it.

325
00:16:36,261 --> 00:16:38,161
She's gone."

326
00:16:38,263 --> 00:16:44,224
And soon after that,
South Jordan police came.

327
00:16:44,336 --> 00:16:50,764
And he sat down.
