337
00:17:26,712 --> 00:17:28,077
Starts at the top
of your head

338
00:17:28,180 --> 00:17:31,081
and goes down
through your whole body

339
00:17:31,183 --> 00:17:33,583
like an electric shock.

340
00:17:34,620 --> 00:17:37,783
And then he showed us
her picture.

341
00:17:39,658 --> 00:17:40,989
<i>And...</i>

342
00:17:42,027 --> 00:17:47,021
<i>...</i> her face was swollen
