to take a lie-detector's test.

365
00:18:59,371 --> 00:19:01,100
I told her that night,
"Just tell them."

366
00:19:01,206 --> 00:19:02,764
I'm like,
"Just tell them the truth.

367
00:19:02,875 --> 00:19:04,172
I can't take this anymore."

368
00:19:04,276 --> 00:19:06,574
I'm like,
"This is killing me inside."

369
00:19:06,678 --> 00:19:08,646
And I guess...
