00:19:18,023 --> 00:19:20,253
So here's the big question,
Jasen.

375
00:19:20,359 --> 00:19:23,624
What do you take responsibility
for from that night?

376
00:19:23,729 --> 00:19:25,720
Everything.
All my actions I did.

377
00:19:25,831 --> 00:19:27,924
I know what I did was wrong.
Absolutely.

378
00:19:28,033 --> 00:19:30,695
I'm not gonna try to deny
anything I did was right.

379
00:19:30,802 --> 00:19:32,997
There's no way
I can justify that.

380
00:19:33,105 --> 00:19:37,701
And then the next morning
when I was supposed to go,

381
00:19:37,809 --> 00:19:40,175
I had woke up and I told my dad
the entire story

382
00:19:40,279 --> 00:19:42,406
about everything
that had happened.

383
00:19:43,982 --> 00:19:48,681
I just remember being
so sick <i>because...</i>

384
00:19:48,787 --> 00:19:51,085
And so sad.

385
00:19:51,190 --> 00:19:53,317
I was so scared to tell my dad
about what had happened.

386
00:19:53,425 --> 00:19:56,622
I was just in a state of shock.

387
00:19:56,728 --> 00:19:59,720
And he ended up crying.

388
00:19:59,831 --> 00:20:02,322
He told me
