396
00:20:32,097 --> 00:20:35,430
And I was so scared.
Scared to death.

397
00:21:18,143 --> 00:21:20,441
I wasn't thinking.

398
00:21:20,545 --> 00:21:23,776
I was completely lost.
I <i>was...</i>

