00:26:42,400 --> 00:26:44,163
Cellphone bills.
Gasoline.

493
00:26:44,269 --> 00:26:45,668
You know?
How much gas are they using?

494
00:26:45,770 --> 00:26:47,829
How many miles are they putting
on their car?

495
00:26:51,843 --> 00:26:53,777
My son designed this tattoo

496
00:26:53,878 --> 00:26:56,506
